name: Seax
tagline: A virtual machine for evaluating FP programs
body:
Seax
====

[![Build Status](https://img.shields.io/travis/hawkw/seax.svg?style=flat-square)](https://travis-ci.org/hawkw/seax) [![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg?style=flat-square)](https://github.com/hawkw/seax/LICENSE)

Seax is a [SECD](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SECD_machine) virtual machine for evaluating FP programs, and a Scheme interpreter targeting that VM. Compilers for other languages targeting this VM are also under consideration.
